metadata.name: Suddenly a cat
metadata.description:
Enjoying a small corner, quiet and tidy and ..... suddenly a cat.

......................................................................................

About "Cyclades Dreams" Collection :

I was born on a small island in Italy, I have island blood. This artwork was taken in July 2010 on various Greek islands in the Cyclades. My vision was to generate a work that seemed like a dream. All images were taken with a Lens Baby.
